Script to schedule the job daily at 10:00 AM, once a week (Friday at 1:00 PM), once a month(Last Friday of the Month at 6:00 PM)

String scheduleTimeDaily = '0 0 10 * * ?';
String scheduleTimeOnceWeek = '0 0 13 ? * 6';
String scheduleOnceMonth = '0 0 18 ? * 6L';
         
SchedulesOpportunitiesBatch sop = new SchedulesOpportunitiesBatch();
         
String jobId = System.schedule('Status of the oportunities', scheduleTimeDaily, SchedulesOpportunitiesBatch);